(44, 1, '2011-09-09 19:37:27', '2011-09-09 19:37:27', '<div class="shadow-inset"><img class="size-full wp-image-148 alignnone" title="display_arc_home" src="http://www.seth-whitaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/display_arc_home.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="480" /></div>\n<div id="portfolio-single-info">\n<h2>Info</h2>\nA complete solution that offers better tools to increase safety, increase productivity and improve customer relations. A touch table will be used on the shop floor to connect to a carâ€™s on board computer and help the mechanic diagnose problems, order parts, and manage tasks. They then use augmented reality safety glasses to repair the car quicker and more efficiently by showing infographics, real time updates on sensor info, and tasks of what to do. Customers can get updates on the progress of their car through a Mobile App, as well as notifications of new issues and approval of part purchases. When the customer returns to pick up their vehicle (or for questions on the repair), the mechanic will walk them through what was done to their car via a Tablet Device. This will help the customer understand what services they are paying for and why.\n\n</div>\n<div class="shadow-inset"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-123" title="display_arc_diagnostic" src="http://www.seth-whitaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/display_arc_diagnostic.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="479" /></div>\n<div class="shadow-inset"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-127" title="display_arc_tablet" src="http://www.seth-whitaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/display_arc_tablet.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="479" /></div>\n<div class="shadow-inset"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-124" title="display_arc_goggles" src="http://www.seth-whitaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/display_arc_goggles.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="309" /></div>\n<div class="shadow-inset"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-126" title="display_arc_mobile" src="http://www.seth-