(96, 1, '2010-05-18 19:57:08', '2010-05-18 19:57:08', '<div class="shadow-inset">\r\n<img src="http://www.seth-whitaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/display_konnekt4-foyer.jpg" alt="" title="display_konnekt4-foyer" width="640" height="409" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-135" />\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="portfolio-single-info">\r\n<h2>Info</h2>\r\nKonnekt 4 is an online multi-player web app game of Connect Four. The application was built in Prototype Javascript, MySQL and PHP. Users must create an account and then can sign into the foyer to see who else is online and challenge them to a game of Konnekt 4. There was use of sessions and cookies to save state and login across pages. I would like to continue developing this game to make it more robust and rewarding to the user.\r\n<p> If you would like to visit the site, head on over <a href="http://seth-whitaker.com/konnekt4/">Here</a>.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="shadow-inset">\r\n<img src="http://www.seth-whitaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/display_konnekt4-game.jpg" alt="" title="display_konnekt4-game" width="640" height="409" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-136" />\r\n</div>', 'Konnekt 4', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'konnekt-4', '', '', '2011-04-14 01:42:20', '2011-04-14 01:42:20', '', 0, 'http://www.seth-whitaker.com/?post_type=portfolio&p=96', 0, 'portfolio', '', 0),
